        <li><strong>Boise City, ID</strong> — RPP approximately 97–101. Has appreciated significantly from a decade of migration but remains below the Pacific Northwest coastal metros. Outdoor recreation access, growing tech scene.</li>
        <li><strong>Albuquerque, NM</strong> — RPP approximately 91–94. Underrated destination; University of New Mexico, National Labs presence, affordable housing, 300+ days of sun, no humidity.</li>
